a:260:{i:0;a:1:{s:2:"id";s:19:"2390932693108233748";}i:1;a:1:{s:10:"short_code";s:11:"CEuTJ3elZYU";}i:2;a:1:{s:12:"created_time";i:1599241409;}i:3;a:1:{s:7:"caption";s:997:"‚ÄúHope‚Äù

Walking through the woods,
I was wondering if there's something missing in this life.
Ultimately concluded it is
The life itself.
The goal was just to live 
To feel free and alive
And not care about anything.
But the dichotomy of wind of our thoughts and the wind of our life happened to be such.
It wasn't possible for any of us  either to sit quietly or to budge.

The goal was to travel,
Travel a lot.
But unfortunately,
Life and everything about it 
Became distorted and vague.
And everyone is trying to dodge this
bullet by baking a cake.

Baffled whether to get 
up or to lay,
Let's not forget the fact that 
after the night comes the day!

.
.
.
